%N A393786 Number of cyclically symmetric planar subpartitions of the size n pyramidal planar partition.
%C A393786 The planar partition having its subpartitions counted is:
%C A393786   n n-1 ... 2 1
%C A393786   n-1 n-2 ... 1
%C A393786   ... ...
%C A393786   2 1
%C A393786   1
%C A393786 A planar partition is said to be totally symmetric if it is invariant by the action of the cyclic group C_3.
%C A393786 The number of all subpartitions regardless of symmetry is given by A115965.
%C A393786 The number of symmetric subpartitions is given by A388969.
%C A393786 The number of totally symmetric subpartitions is given by A393748.
%H A393786 Ludovic Schwob, <a href="/A393786/a393786.txt">SageMath program</a>
